data.title: US Electric Power Transmission Lines in Paulding County, Georgia
data.meta_description: Access detailed GIS data on the overhead AC electric power transmission line in Paulding County, Georgia, operated by Georgia Power Co, including voltage and substation information.
data.text:
Access precise and up-to-date GIS data for your projects with our US Electric Power Transmission Lines dataset focused on Paulding County, Georgia. This specific dataset offers detailed information about the transmission lines used for bulk electric power transmission and control, indicating their operational status as operational and overhead. Managed by Georgia Power Co, this dataset includes entries such as the Bowen Substation and Villa Rica, highlighted with characteristics like voltage levels listed at 500 kV. Professionals can benefit from the dataset's sourced and verified data as of 2015, ensuring accuracy for analysis and planning. Ideal for those involved in utility management and geographical analysis within the region.
